1
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:45,220
Compared to her contributions,

2
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,810
what we've done

3
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,900
is nothing.

4
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,340
It's pointless

5
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,850
to say those compliments here.

6
00:01:50,850 --> 00:01:52,650
Go say them in Beijing if you can.

7
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:57,850
Why aren't you eating?

8
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,120
Is it not good?

9
00:01:59,210 --> 00:02:00,740
It's good. It's delicious.

10
00:02:01,810 --> 00:02:03,740
Just looking at it makes me hungry.

11
00:02:50,130 --> 00:02:50,930
What's wrong?

12
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:52,520
Can't sleep?

13
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:55,000
Did I wake you?

14
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,280
No.

15
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,800
I haven't gone to bed yet.

16
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:01,210
I just...

17
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,080
dreamed of Dolma.

18
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,710
She must be cheering you on.

19
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:13,500
She asked me

20
00:03:14,370 --> 00:03:16,170
if we had given up on mining there

21
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:18,870
and if I was going to let

22
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:21,000
the information she died for be buried

23
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:24,120
in Bolamula forever.

24
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:29,360
I couldn't answer her.

25
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:33,630
You can show her

26
00:03:34,020 --> 00:03:35,220
the report we've made

27
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:38,740
and tell her about what we've experienced.

28
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:43,190
When dealing with others,

29
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,210
I have countless reasons

30
00:03:44,210 --> 00:03:45,210
to convince them.

31
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,590
But when facing Dolma,

32
00:03:49,740 --> 00:03:51,340
I even doubt

33
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,680
whether what I've insisted on for so long

34
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,690
is right

35
00:03:56,690 --> 00:03:57,970
or wrong.

36
00:04:04,460 --> 00:04:05,630
I don't know Dolma,

37
00:04:06,630 --> 00:04:07,960
so I can't speak for her.

38
00:04:10,210 --> 00:04:11,080
But

39
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,480
would the Bolamula of her dreams

40
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,269
be a place full of gullies

41
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:21,230
where all living beings have been devastated?

42
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,300
Whether it's Dolma,

43
00:04:29,630 --> 00:04:30,620
Lin,

44
00:04:32,220 --> 00:04:35,080
or other colleagues in the County Party Committee,

45
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:37,310
everyone's love

46
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:38,540
for this land

47
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:39,860
is no less than mine.

48
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:46,690
But why

49
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,570
are our understandings

50
00:04:47,570 --> 00:04:48,770
so different?

51
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,370
Sometimes I'm afraid...

52
00:04:58,510 --> 00:05:00,510
afraid that I'm the one who's wrong.

53
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,560
If...

54
00:05:11,310 --> 00:05:12,740
we can't even protect

55
00:05:12,810 --> 00:05:14,810
the living creatures in this place,

56
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:17,870
how can we claim to love it?

57
00:05:21,060 --> 00:05:22,070
The old me

58
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,420
might

59
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,390
have doubted

60
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,830
and wavered.

61
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,750
But now,

62
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,560
I have only one answer.

63
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:39,190
I'm

64
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:40,450
proud of

65
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,560
what we are doing.

66
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:45,159
I'm proud of you.

67
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:52,270
Thank you.

68
00:05:56,250 --> 00:05:56,740
You're acting

69
00:05:56,740 --> 00:05:58,540
more and more like a captain now.

70
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,390
Duo, are you alright?

71
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:05,740
Han said

72
00:06:05,810 --> 00:06:07,270
the same thing to me today.

73
00:06:08,370 --> 00:06:09,920
But he only said

74
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,500
I'm like a deputy captain.

75
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,420
Besides,

76
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:15,430
in the team,

77
00:06:15,830 --> 00:06:16,370
I'm not

78
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,010
the strongest physically,

79
00:06:18,810 --> 00:06:20,070
nor do I have the ability

80
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:21,010
to make everyone's lives

81
00:06:21,010 --> 00:06:21,860
better.

82
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:24,420
I'm just

83
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,330
an ordinary

84
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:27,690
police officer.

85
00:06:30,250 --> 00:06:31,180
You never needed

86
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:32,250
to be like a scout

87
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,690
in the Mountain Patrol.

88
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:37,470
Out there in the Uninhabited Zone,

89
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,510
you embody the law for us.

90
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:41,510
If you hadn't stopped

91
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:42,870
He back then,

92
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:45,360
we might have done

93
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,330
the same things as the poachers.

94
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:52,020
We all have to thank you for that.

95
00:07:09,010 --> 00:07:09,500
Look.

96
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:11,250
A little medal.

97
00:07:13,390 --> 00:07:14,300
I have one too.

98
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,190
You've been in the Mountain Patrol

99
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:32,500
for over a year, right?

100
00:07:34,930 --> 00:07:36,659
It's been a year and ten months.

101
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:41,950
Sometimes I feel like

102
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:43,550
the days in the mountains...

103
00:07:45,180 --> 00:07:46,710
are longer than a lifetime.

104
00:07:50,190 --> 00:07:50,930
Yeah.

105
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,020
When I'm in the mountains,

106
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,180
I just want to come back soon.

107
00:07:58,130 --> 00:07:59,560
But after a few days back,

108
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:02,190
I'm already thinking about

109
00:08:02,330 --> 00:08:04,130
going into the mountains again.

110
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:23,180
Want it?

111
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:25,280
No, thanks.

112
00:08:35,289 --> 00:08:36,750
Let's go up and have a look.

113
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,100
A meeting of the Standing Committee.

114
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:41,360
It's not appropriate.

115
00:08:46,290 --> 00:08:48,220
The topic of today's meeting

116
00:08:48,530 --> 00:08:49,320
is to decide

117
00:08:49,460 --> 00:08:50,740
whether to submit Mr. Lin Peisheng's

118
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:52,360
development zone application report

119
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,580
or Mr. Duojie's

120
00:08:53,650 --> 00:08:54,770
reserve application report

121
00:08:54,770 --> 00:08:55,740
to the city.

122
00:08:56,530 --> 00:08:57,620
I hope you all

123
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:59,500
can approach this objectively,

124
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,240
without

125
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,460
emotional bias.

126
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:03,910
County Mayor Lin.

127
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:08,700
Mr. Duojie's report

128
00:09:08,770 --> 00:09:10,220
provides significant guidance

129
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:11,980
for the development zone planning.

130
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:13,510
Incorporating his report,

131
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:14,750
I've made some adjustments

132
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:16,250
to my development zone plan

133
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:17,910
and formed two new proposals.

134
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,100
Now,

135
00:09:19,860 --> 00:09:21,720
I'd like to discuss them with you.

136
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,090
The first proposal:

137
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:26,980
we'll start by

138
00:09:27,220 --> 00:09:28,720
bringing in high-quality industrial and mining enterprises,

139
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,910
focusing on development

140
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:31,240
for three to five years.

141
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:33,130
To fully boost the economy.

142
00:09:33,130 --> 00:09:34,150
Let's remove our county's

143
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:34,890
"impoverished county" label

144
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:35,740
first.

145
00:09:36,290 --> 00:09:38,080
Once the county's finances have strengthened

146
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,010
and people's lives have improved,

147
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:41,480
we will then submit

148
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,150
the application report

149
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:45,200
for establishing a nature reserve to the higher authorities.

150
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,580
I mentioned in my report

151
00:09:47,250 --> 00:09:48,390
that the Tibetan antelope population

152
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,080
has already reached

153
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,480
the brink of extinction.

154
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:52,270
In another three to five years,

155
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:53,340
they might

156
00:09:53,460 --> 00:09:54,270
disappear from the planet

157
00:09:54,270 --> 00:09:55,220
forever.

158
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,000
Those are all estimates you made

159
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,260
based on the situation

160
00:09:58,290 --> 00:09:59,130
in the past.

161
00:09:59,630 --> 00:10:01,090
Things are different now.

162
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,340
The largest

163
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:03,720
illegal mining and poaching gang

164
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,460
in Bolamula

165
00:10:04,530 --> 00:10:05,960
has been taken down.

166
00:10:06,650 --> 00:10:07,170
Also,

167
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:08,840
the County Forestry Police

168
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,960
will be established soon,

169
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,170
so the  problem of insufficient police force

170
00:10:11,170 --> 00:10:12,170
will be resolved.

171
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:12,980
Plus,

172
00:10:13,050 --> 00:10:14,150
with our administration

173
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:15,010
of the development zone...

174
00:10:15,010 --> 00:10:15,910
What makes you think

175
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:16,670
that Li Yongqiang's gang

176
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:17,910
is the biggest gang?

177
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:20,150
I've been in there for over two years.

178
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:22,240
and I still wouldn't dare make that judgment.

179
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,150
Do you know

180
00:10:23,250 --> 00:10:24,860
how many routes there are into Bolamula?

181
00:10:24,860 --> 00:10:26,240
How many checkpoints

182
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:27,170
can a county forestry police force set up?

183
00:10:27,170 --> 00:10:27,910
Mr. Duojie!

184
00:10:29,150 --> 00:10:30,200
Mr. Lin Peisheng.

185
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:32,220
As I have said before,

186
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:34,080
let us discuss this rationally

187
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,410
and set emotions aside.

188
00:10:35,890 --> 00:10:36,370
Okay.

189
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,240
Let me present the second proposal.

190
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:40,750
We will submit

191
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:43,430
the application report for establishing

192
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:45,000
a nature reserve to our superiors

193
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,600
right now.

194
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,240
However,

195
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:47,830
the reserve's scope

196
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:49,660
must be significantly reduced.

197
00:10:50,170 --> 00:10:51,100
Bolamula covers

198
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,460
more than 40,000 square kilometers.

199
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:53,250
A one-size-fits-all approach

200
00:10:53,250 --> 00:10:54,770
would be irresponsible.

201
00:10:55,700 --> 00:10:56,200
Based on

202
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,770
the development zone application report's data

203
00:10:57,770 --> 00:10:59,230
regarding mineral types,

204
00:10:59,250 --> 00:11:00,630
distribution of mineral veins,

205
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:01,890
and mineral reserves,

206
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:02,910
combined with

207
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,720
the reserve application report's information

208
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,460
on Tibetan antelope migration routes,

209
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:08,590
climate, and hydrological features,

210
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:10,350
I've devised a compromise.

211
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:11,130
That is,

212
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,340
to limit the reserve's area

213
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:13,940
to

214
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:16,210
within 20,000 square kilometers.

215
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:19,360
Of course.

216
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:22,110
If we adopt this proposal,

217
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:24,130
economic development will proceed

218
00:11:24,130 --> 00:11:25,660
more slowly than expected.

219
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,510
But considering

220
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:28,750
the unique ecological importance

221
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:30,510
of the Qinghai-Tibet Plateau

222
00:11:30,620 --> 00:11:31,940
to the entire country,

223
00:11:32,010 --> 00:11:33,150
slowing down a bit

224
00:11:33,910 --> 00:11:35,370
is worth it, in my opinion.

225
00:11:35,890 --> 00:11:37,270
This is worth considering.

226
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:38,940
I agree with this too.

227
00:11:39,010 --> 00:11:39,820
I agree too.

228
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,050
This is

229
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:43,750
a good solution that balances both interests.

230
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:49,100
Deputy County Mayor Duo,

231
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,240
what do you think?

232
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,180
Wishful thinking.

233
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:56,770
All armchair strategy.

234
00:11:56,770 --> 00:11:57,890
Mr. Duojie!

235
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,890
Secretary Chen,

236
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:04,150
County Mayor Lin.

237
00:12:06,820 --> 00:12:07,770
What I'm about to say

238
00:12:07,770 --> 00:12:09,170
is not driven by emotion.

239
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:11,100
During this time,

240
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:12,230
I've been thinking—

241
00:12:13,170 --> 00:12:15,100
can development and conservation

242
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:17,100
truly coexist

243
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,940
in Bolamula?

244
00:12:19,890 --> 00:12:20,440
Like

245
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,750
all of you here,

246
00:12:22,530 --> 00:12:23,170
I hope

247
00:12:23,250 --> 00:12:23,910
we can find

248
00:12:24,010 --> 00:12:26,340
a solution that balances both interests.

249
00:12:27,010 --> 00:12:28,540
But I can't deceive myself.

250
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,890
County Mayor Lin, you keep emphasizing

251
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:33,620
scientific,

252
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,730
meticulous,

253
00:12:34,820 --> 00:12:36,020
and moderate mining.

254
00:12:36,620 --> 00:12:37,840
Given our current human resources

255
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,410
and management capabilities,

256
00:12:39,410 --> 00:12:40,100
what makes you think

257
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:41,230
we can achieve that?

258
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,700
And what makes you believe

259
00:12:42,790 --> 00:12:44,080
the large industrial and mining enterprises

260
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,010
you're bringing in

261
00:12:45,010 --> 00:12:46,150
will comply?

262
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:47,500
This is precisely the challenge

263
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:47,980
that tests

264
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:49,580
our capabilities as managers.

265
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:50,390
The Party and the people

266
00:12:50,390 --> 00:12:51,450
have placed us here

267
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,030
precisely to

268
00:12:52,030 --> 00:12:54,030
shoulder these responsibilities.

269
00:12:54,390 --> 00:12:55,200
Solving these problems

270
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,360
is our duty.

271
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:02,400
Bolamula

272
00:13:02,460 --> 00:13:03,590
is a treasure trove.

273
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:05,390
Once its doors

274
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,510
are opened,

275
00:13:07,050 --> 00:13:07,710
it will test

276
00:13:07,790 --> 00:13:08,500
not only

277
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:09,840
us as administrators

278
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:11,820
but also

279
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:13,710
the darkest, most greedy nature

280
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:15,050
of every person

281
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,890
who enters  it.

282
00:13:22,530 --> 00:13:24,260
A single Tibetan antelope pelt

283
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:25,630
can sell for 600 yuan

284
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:26,910
to a street trader

285
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:29,030
on National Highway 109.

286
00:13:30,170 --> 00:13:31,770
When smuggled to South Asia,

287
00:13:31,770 --> 00:13:33,770
the price skyrockets to 3,000 yuan!

288
00:13:33,820 --> 00:13:35,220
Yet, made into a Shahtoosh shawl,

289
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:36,290
one can sell for

290
00:13:36,580 --> 00:13:37,410
up to 40,000 US dollars

291
00:13:37,410 --> 00:13:39,340
in European and American markets!

292
00:13:39,550 --> 00:13:39,750
But

293
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:41,320
the cost to obtain a pelt

294
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:43,720
is only seven to ten yuan.

295
00:13:46,220 --> 00:13:47,880
According to Marxist theory,

296
00:13:48,250 --> 00:13:49,410
when a business's profit

297
00:13:49,410 --> 00:13:50,700
reaches 300 percent,

298
00:13:51,410 --> 00:13:52,910
capital will dare to commit any crime,

299
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:53,910
trample all laws,

300
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:54,550
and even risk

301
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,720
being hanged!

302
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,040
And the profit from poaching

303
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:01,740
is far more than 300 percent.

304
00:14:08,630 --> 00:14:09,600
I sincerely urge you, comrades,

305
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:11,130
to consider this carefully

306
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:13,010
and not become the sinners

307
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:15,450
who open this treasure trove.

308
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:40,870
Discussions about human nature...

309
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,410
are endless.

310
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:46,170
The debate over

311
00:14:46,170 --> 00:14:47,500
whether human nature is

312
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:49,320
Mencius, axe.

313
00:14:49,410 --> 00:14:51,030
has persisted since the time of Mencius and Xunzi,

314
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:52,890
yet there's still no conclusion.

315
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:53,860
As for the direction

316
00:14:53,860 --> 00:14:55,460
Mazhi County should take...

317
00:14:57,050 --> 00:14:57,720
I suggest

318
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,620
we decide by democratic vote.

319
00:15:05,250 --> 00:15:05,870
Alright.

320
00:15:09,940 --> 00:15:11,400
All in favor of submitting

321
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,320
the development zone application report to the city,

322
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,720
please raise your hands.

323
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:21,870
Four votes.

324
00:15:24,370 --> 00:15:25,390
All in favor of submitting

325
00:15:25,390 --> 00:15:27,650
the nature reserve application report,

326
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:30,220
please raise your hands.

327
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:43,340
Mr. Duojie,

328
00:15:44,270 --> 00:15:45,580
what is your decision?

329
00:15:53,550 --> 00:15:54,290
I abstain.

330
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:57,770
What do you mean?

331
00:15:58,580 --> 00:15:59,200
Wasn't the reserve

332
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,580
your proposal?

333
00:16:05,370 --> 00:16:06,170
I believe...

334
00:16:07,790 --> 00:16:08,340
we should not

335
00:16:08,340 --> 00:16:09,670
make this decision now.

336
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:15,050
Once this step is taken,

337
00:16:16,250 --> 00:16:17,600
recovering from it

338
00:16:19,010 --> 00:16:19,870
would take at least

339
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:21,050
hundreds of years.

340
00:16:23,130 --> 00:16:24,080
That cost

341
00:16:25,290 --> 00:16:26,220
is not something

342
00:16:26,220 --> 00:16:27,130
the few of us here

343
00:16:27,130 --> 00:16:28,120
can bear.

344
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:32,550
On this trip to Beijing,

345
00:16:33,220 --> 00:16:35,620
besides giving lectures at universities,

346
00:16:35,790 --> 00:16:36,460
I'll meet with

347
00:16:36,460 --> 00:16:38,910
leaders and experts from the Ministry of Forestry.

348
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:40,080
I'll ask them for feedback

349
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:40,890
on my report.

350
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:44,860
I'll also bring

351
00:16:44,860 --> 00:16:47,190
the development zone application report

352
00:16:47,650 --> 00:16:49,580
to environmental

353
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:51,270
and geological experts

354
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:53,740
and have them do an assessment together.

355
00:16:57,050 --> 00:16:57,620
County Mayor Lin

356
00:16:57,620 --> 00:16:59,840
has been proposing to build a development zone

357
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:00,840
for three years.

358
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,420
We've waited three years.

359
00:17:06,530 --> 00:17:07,510
We can also wait

360
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:09,700
another month or two.

361
00:17:19,589 --> 00:17:20,589
Party Secretary.

362
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:21,599
Director.

363
00:17:22,980 --> 00:17:23,640
Uncle Lin.

364
00:17:24,030 --> 00:17:24,329
No...

365
00:17:24,329 --> 00:17:25,329
County Mayor Lin.

366
00:17:25,609 --> 00:17:26,609
County Mayor Lin.

367
00:17:30,810 --> 00:17:32,610
Looks like the results are good.

368
00:17:35,310 --> 00:17:36,000
How was it?

369
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:38,370
You're a Party member.

370
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:39,510
Don't pry.

371
00:17:44,810 --> 00:17:45,330
Duojie.

372
00:17:48,610 --> 00:17:49,540
Have a safe trip.

373
00:17:50,290 --> 00:17:51,150
Come back soon.

374
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:52,750
Okay.

375
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:53,770
Goodbye.

376
00:17:54,700 --> 00:17:56,230
Goodbye, County Mayor Lin.

377
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:09,150
Deputy County Mayor Duo, hello.

378
00:18:26,510 --> 00:18:27,220
Hey.

379
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:29,340
This knife is exquisite.

380
00:18:29,380 --> 00:18:30,440
Did you just buy it?

381
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:32,650
It's still Dolma's.

382
00:18:33,660 --> 00:18:34,330
Tashi had someone make

383
00:18:34,330 --> 00:18:36,460
a new sheath with a leather strap for it

384
00:18:36,660 --> 00:18:38,200
and insisted on giving it to me.

385
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,010
It's not appropriate

386
00:18:39,010 --> 00:18:40,240
